*graylog2-0.9.6 (28 Aug 2012)

  28 Aug 2012; Dean Matzkov <bapabooiee@gmail.com> +graylog2-0.9.6.ebuild,
  +files/graylog2-0.9.6.initd, -files/graylog2.initd-r1,
  -graylog2-0.9.4_p1.ebuild, +files/graylog2-0.9.6.confd:
  Version bump. Changes include installing a conf.d file and adding a
  post-install message that informs users about Graylog2 moving to
  ElasticSearch.

  10 Feb 2011; Dean Matzkov <bapabooiee@gmail.com> -files/graylog2.confd,
  -graylog2-0.9.3.ebuild, -graylog2-0.9.3-r1.ebuild, -graylog2-0.9.4.ebuild,
  graylog2-0.9.4_p1.ebuild, -files/graylog2.initd, graylog2-0.9.4_p1-r1.ebuild:
  Removed old ebuilds+files, and did some minor cleanup.

  24 Jan 2011; Dean Matzkov (bapa) <bapabooiee@gmail.com> +metadata.xml,
  +files/graylog2.initd-r2, +graylog2-0.9.4_p1-r1.ebuild:
  Tweaked the description and post-install message; created a `local-mongodb'
  USE flag to signify a local MongoDB installation is intended; polished-up the
  init script; changed configuration file's default permissions.

*graylog2-0.9.4_p1 (16 Jan 2011)

  16 Jan 2011; Dean Matzkov <bapabooiee@gmail.com> graylog2-0.9.4.ebuild,
  +graylog2-0.9.4_p1.ebuild:
  Version bump

*graylog2-0.9.4 (15 Jan 2011)

  15 Jan 2011; Dean Matzkov <bapabooiee@gmail.com> graylog2-0.9.3.ebuild,
  graylog2-0.9.3-r1.ebuild, +graylog2-0.9.4.ebuild:
  Version bump, and fixed download URI in all ebuilds.

*graylog2-0.9.3-r1 (15 Jan 2011)

  15 Jan 2011; Dean Matzkov <bapabooiee@gmail.com> files/graylog2.initd,
  -graylog2-0.9.1.ebuild, -graylog2-0.9.2.ebuild, +graylog2-0.9.3-r1.ebuild,
  +files/graylog2.initd-r1:
  Removed older versions, and revised ebuild. Changes include:

  * Removing dependency on MongoDB, because the server won't always be local.
  * Revised /etc/init.d/graylog2.
  * Removed need for /etc/conf.d/graylog2 file.

*graylog2-0.9.3 (24 Dec 2010)

  24 Dec 2010; Dean Matzkov <bapabooiee@gmail.com> +graylog2-0.9.3.ebuild:
  Version bump

